						<div class="postbody">Theoretically, emulating PPUSTATUS ($2002), PPUSCROLL ($2005), and PPUADDR ($2006) with cycle accuracy requires rendering with cycle accuracy because something might change the scroll position and thus the pixels under sprite 0, causing sprite 0 not to be triggered and PPUSTATUS to be incorrect.</div>

